---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../../sections/home-one/Section1-Header.astro';
import FooterFour from '../../sections/shared/FooterFour.astro';
import ServiceHeroFullwidth from '../../sections/service/ServiceHeroFullwidth.astro';
import BreadcrumbSchema from '../../components/seo/BreadcrumbSchema.astro';
import { getMediaSlot } from '../../lib/media';
import { SITE_URL } from '../../lib/seo';

const heroImage = await getMediaSlot('sidecar-tours.hero.image', '/assets/img/transfers/rhodes-transfer-hero.jpg');
const bodyImg1 = await getMediaSlot('sidecar-tours.body.img-1', '/assets/img/transfers/transfer-rider.jpg');
const bodyImg2 = await getMediaSlot('sidecar-tours.body.img-2', '/assets/img/transfers/transfer-sidecar.jpg');
---

<BaseLayout title="Rhodes Sidecar Tours — The Most Unique Experience in Rhodes | Rhodes Rent a Boat" description="Rhodes Sidecar Tours is one of the most unique things to do in Rhodes. Explore the island in a vintage sidecar motorcycle with a local driver. Panoramic views, hidden locations and unforgettable memories." ogImage={heroImage} canonical={`${SITE_URL}/service/rhodes-sidecar-tours`}>
  <BreadcrumbSchema items={[
    { name: 'Home', url: '/' },
    { name: 'Things to Do', url: '/things-to-do' },
    { name: 'Rhodes Sidecar Tours', url: '/things-to-do/rhodes-sidecar-tours' },
  ]} />
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    '@context': 'https://schema.org',
    '@type': 'TouristAttraction',
    name: 'Rhodes Sidecar Tours',
    description: 'Vintage sidecar motorcycle tours in Rhodes with a local driver — panoramic views, hidden locations and unforgettable memories.',
    url: `${SITE_URL}/things-to-do/rhodes-sidecar-tours`,
    image: heroImage.startsWith('http') ? heroImage : `${SITE_URL}${heroImage}`,
    touristType: ['Adventure traveler', 'Cultural traveler', 'Couples', 'Solo traveler'],
    isAccessibleForFree: false,
    address: {
      '@type': 'PostalAddress',
      addressLocality: 'Rhodes',
      addressRegion: 'South Aegean',
      addressCountry: 'GR',
    },
  })} is:inline />
  <Header />

  <!-- 1. Hero -->
  <ServiceHeroFullwidth
    title="Rhodes Sidecar Tours"
    subtitle="One of the Most Unique Experiences in Rhodes"
    backgroundImage={heroImage}
  />

  <!-- 2. Article -->
  <article style="padding: 60px 0 40px;">
    <div class="container">
      <div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">

        <h1 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.2rem); font-weight: 700; color: #113D48; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.3;" data-ani="slideinup">The Best Thing to Do in Rhodes Island – Rhodes Sidecar Tours</h1>

        <p style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-style: italic; font-size: 1.15rem; line-height: 1.7; color: #1CA8CB; margin-bottom: 32px; padding-bottom: 32px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;" data-ani="fadein">
          Rhodes is not only an island you explore by car. It is an island you experience through its roads, landscapes and hidden places. And a sidecar is one of the most unique ways to experience it.
        </p>

        <div class="sc-article" data-ani="fadein" data-ani-delay="0.1">
          <p>When visiting Rhodes, most people think about beaches, boat trips and the Old Town. While all of these are beautiful experiences, there is one activity on the island that is completely different and offers a unique way to explore Rhodes.</p>

          <p><strong style="color: #113D48;">Rhodes Sidecar Tours</strong> is one of the most unique experiences you can have on the island. Instead of sitting in a bus or renting a car, you explore Rhodes in a vintage sidecar motorcycle driven by a local driver who knows the island very well.</p>

          <!-- Image 1 -->
          <div style="margin: 32px 0; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden;">
            <img src={bodyImg1} alt="Rhodes sidecar tour experience" style="width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 16/9; object-fit: cover; display: block;" loading="lazy" />
          </div>

          <p>The experience is not just transportation or a tour. It is a journey around Rhodes with panoramic views, coastal roads, mountain routes and hidden locations that many visitors would never find on their own.</p>

          <h2 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.35rem; font-weight: 700; color: #113D48; margin: 32px 0 16px;">What You Will See</h2>
          <p>During a sidecar tour, visitors can explore Rhodes Town, the Old Town walls, Mandraki Harbour, Monte Smith, hidden viewpoints, small villages and scenic coastal roads. There are also sunset tours and longer tours that explore the countryside and mountains of Rhodes.</p>

          <!-- Image 2 -->
          <div style="margin: 32px 0; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden;">
            <img src={bodyImg2} alt="Vintage sidecar motorcycle in Rhodes" style="width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 16/9; object-fit: cover; display: block;" loading="lazy" />
          </div>

          <h2 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.35rem; font-weight: 700; color: #113D48; margin: 32px 0 16px;">A Slow, Personal Experience</h2>
          <p>The sidecar experience is slow, relaxed and very personal. It is not a mass tour and not a typical excursion. It is a private experience designed for visitors who want to see Rhodes in a different way and create unforgettable memories.</p>

          <h2 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.35rem; font-weight: 700; color: #113D48; margin: 32px 0 16px;">Who Is This For?</h2>
          <p>Rhodes Sidecar Tours is ideal for:</p>
          <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 6px 24px; margin: 16px 0 24px;" class="sc-list-grid">
            <p style="margin: 0; padding: 6px 0;"><i class="fas fa-check" style="color: #1CA8CB; margin-right: 8px; font-size: 0.8rem;"></i>Couples</p>
            <p style="margin: 0; padding: 6px 0;"><i class="fas fa-check" style="color: #1CA8CB; margin-right: 8px; font-size: 0.8rem;"></i>Families</p>
            <p style="margin: 0; padding: 6px 0;"><i class="fas fa-check" style="color: #1CA8CB; margin-right: 8px; font-size: 0.8rem;"></i>Photographers</p>
            <p style="margin: 0; padding: 6px 0;"><i class="fas fa-check" style="color: #1CA8CB; margin-right: 8px; font-size: 0.8rem;"></i>Unique experience lovers</p>
            <p style="margin: 0; padding: 6px 0;"><i class="fas fa-check" style="color: #1CA8CB; margin-right: 8px; font-size: 0.8rem;"></i>Beyond typical tourism</p>
            <p style="margin: 0; padding: 6px 0;"><i class="fas fa-check" style="color: #1CA8CB; margin-right: 8px; font-size: 0.8rem;"></i>Sunset seekers</p>
          </div>

          <p style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.05rem; color: #113D48; text-align: center; padding: 24px 0; margin: 28px 0; border-top: 1px solid #eee; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; line-height: 1.7;">
            If you are looking for something different, something memorable and something truly unique — this is one of the most special things you can do in Rhodes.
          </p>

          <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 32px;">
            <p style="font-size: 1rem; color: #4a5568; margin-bottom: 20px;">Learn more about this experience:</p>
            <a href="https://www.rhodessidecartours.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="th-btn style3 th-icon">Visit RhodesSidecarTours.com <i class="fas fa-external-link-alt" style="margin-left: 6px; font-size: 0.8rem;"></i></a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>

  <!-- 3. Back + Related -->
  <section style="padding: 40px 0 60px; background: #f8fafb;">
    <div class="container">
      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="/things-to-do" style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 600; color: #1CA8CB; text-decoration: none;"><i class="fa-regular fa-arrow-left"></i> Back to Best Boat Tours in Rhodes</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 4. Contact -->
  <section style="padding: 80px 0; background: #113D48;">
    <div class="container">
      <div style="max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center;">
        <h2 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem); font-weight: 700; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 20px;" data-ani="slideinup">Looking for More Unique Experiences?</h2>
        <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); margin-bottom: 36px;" data-ani="fadein" data-ani-delay="0.1">
          If you want to discover more unique things to do in Rhodes beyond the typical tourist routes, contact us and we will share our best local recommendations.
        </p>
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 16px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;" data-ani="slideinup" data-ani-delay="0.2">
          <a href="/contact" class="th-btn style3 th-icon">Send Us a Message</a>
          <a href="https://wa.me/302241012345" style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding: 14px 28px; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; color: #fff; border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3); border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.3s ease;"><i class="fab fa-whatsapp"></i> WhatsApp</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <FooterFour />
</BaseLayout>

<script>
</script>

<style>
  .sc-article {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: #4a5568;
  }

  .sc-article p {
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 575px) {
    .sc-list-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr !important;
    }
  }
</style>
